flowchart TD
    T["Microsoft Outlook Trigger
    (new emails)"]
    LLM["Basic LLM Chain
    (classify with AI)"]
    GF["Outlook: Get Many Folders"]
    MG["Merge
    (Append)"]
    CODE["Code: find folder ID"]
    MV["Outlook: Move Message"]
    IF["IF: category == urgent"]
    TG["Telegram: Send Message
    (urgent email)"]

    T --> LLM --> MG
    T --> GF --> MG
    MG --> CODE --> MV
    MV --> IF -->|true| TG
